
# Day 10: Terraform Loops & Conditionals — Dynamic Infrastructure

## Overview

On Day 10, I refactored my Terraform code to eliminate repetition and make the infrastructure more dynamic and scalable. I implemented Terraform loop constructs (`count`, `for_each`, `for` expressions) and conditional logic to control resource creation and configuration.

I also enhanced the webserver cluster module by introducing an autoscaling toggle and environment-based configuration.

---

